---
title: Carb Smart Double Pork Chops with Creamy Green Beans
description: This dinner screams comfort food! Creamy stove-top beans are topped with perfectly seared pork chops, perfect for a fall evening.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-cotelettes-de-porc-743808a7.jpg
